text:
Hungry Hamster's Gallery in Singapore!
Find the artist's art prints, paintings, art toys and more in this booth located inside Co-Play Singapore.
Definitely a must go if you want to look for something from a local artist.

Hungry Hamster is in Singapore!! Drop by level 3 Plaza Singapura at Co-Play to check out Freddy’s amazing collection of adorable hamsters! I picked up the “Willing Sacrifice”, which is sitting snugly at home, freakin love it!
Great authentic and original art and designer toys
